title: [Yegharren Plain, Wooded Trail]
description: The trail winds down the hillside into a wooded valley, the dense underbrush threatening to cover the path and obscure the way.  Smells of woods and dirt and moss fill the shaded air, and a clear patch of open moonlit sky is visible to the east.
